"       Section Editor",
"      </a>",
"      <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?24/15/24818/contributors\" id=\"se952\">",
"       Jonathan Corren, MD",
"      </a>",
"     </td>",
"     <td>",
